---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
import ExampleSection from '../../components/ExampleSection.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Shell Layout" description="Complete application layout structure.">
  <article class="space-y-12">
    <header class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Shell Layout</h1>
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full border bg-success/10 text-success border-success/30">stable</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
        The shell layout provides the structural foundation for the entire application, including header, sidebars, main content area, and optional footer.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Product Availability -->
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Product Availability</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#4C92D9]"></span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">CP</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Header, Left (2), Right (3), No Footer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#4C92D9]"></span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">VP</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Header, Left, Right, Footer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#30659F]"></span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">PPM</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Header, Left, Right, Footer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-surface">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#804A98]"></span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Maconomy</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Header, Left, Right, Footer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CP Structure Overview -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">CP Structure Overview</h2>
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-theme-primary/10 text-theme-primary rounded">CP/VP</span>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        The CP shell features a header, two-panel left sidebar, three-panel right sidebar, and no footer. 
        Sidebars are docked to the edges with an 8px gap from the header.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Visual Diagram -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-obsidian">
        <div class="relative bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden" style="height: 320px;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-11 bg-white dark:bg-surface border-b border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Header (44px)</span>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Content Area with Gap -->
          <div class="absolute top-[52px] left-0 right-0 bottom-0 flex">
            <!-- Left Sidebar - Docked to left edge -->
            <div class="w-14 flex flex-col gap-4 py-2">
              <!-- Panel 1 -->
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-tr-xl rounded-br-xl shadow-lg flex-none h-24 flex items-center justify-center border border-l-0 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Panel 1</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Panel 2 -->
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-tr-xl rounded-br-xl shadow-lg flex-1 flex items-center justify-center border border-l-0 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Panel 2</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Main Content -->
            <div class="flex-1 m-2 bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400">Main Content</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Right Sidebar - Docked to right edge -->
            <div class="w-14 flex flex-col gap-3 py-2">
              <!-- Panel 1 -->
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg flex-none h-20 flex items-center justify-center border border-r-0 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Panel 1</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Panel 2 -->
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg flex-none h-14 flex items-center justify-center border border-r-0 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Panel 2</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Panel 3 -->
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg flex-1 flex items-center justify-center border border-r-0 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Panel 3</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap indicator -->
          <div class="absolute top-11 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] text-theme-primary font-mono bg-theme-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" /></svg>
            8px gap
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Legend -->
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-xs">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-white dark:bg-surface rounded shadow border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"></div>
            <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Panels with shadow</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-tr rounded-br border-2 border-l-0 border-theme-primary"></div>
            <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Left: rounded inner corners</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-tl rounded-bl border-2 border-r-0 border-theme-primary"></div>
            <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Right: rounded inner corners</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CP Code Example -->
      <CodeBlock 
        language="html"
        filename="cp-shell-layout.html"
        code={`<div class="flex flex-col h-screen bg-slate-100 dark:bg-obsidian">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="h-11 bg-white dark:bg-surface border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border shrink-0">
    <!-- Header content -->
  </header>
  
  <!-- Content wrapper (8px gap from header via pt-2) -->
  <div class="flex flex-1 overflow-hidden pt-2">
    <!-- Left Sidebar - Docked to left edge -->
    <aside class="w-[52px] flex flex-col gap-4 shrink-0">
      <!-- Panel 1: Primary nav -->
      <div class="bg-[#fcfdff] rounded-tr-xl rounded-br-xl shadow-lg">
        <!-- 4 icon buttons -->
      </div>
      <!-- Panel 2: Secondary nav -->
      <div class="bg-[#fcfdff] rounded-tr-xl rounded-br-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
        <!-- 11 icon buttons with divider -->
      </div>
    </aside>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto mx-2">
      <!-- Page content -->
    </main>
    
    <!-- Right Sidebar - Docked to right edge -->
    <aside class="w-[52px] flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
      <!-- Panel 1: Logo + notifications -->
      <div class="bg-[#fcfdff] rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg">
        <!-- Logo, Bell, Files icons -->
      </div>
      <!-- Panel 2: Tools -->
      <div class="bg-[#fcfdff] rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg">
        <!-- Print, Layout icons -->
      </div>
      <!-- Panel 3: Settings -->
      <div class="bg-[#fcfdff] rounded-tl-xl rounded-bl-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
        <!-- Mic, Signal, Actions, Help icons -->
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
  
  <!-- No footer for CP -->
</div>`}
      />
    </section>

    <!-- Key Specifications -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Key Specifications</h2>
      
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Property</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Value</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Notes</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Header height</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">44px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Fixed, does not scroll</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Gap from header</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">8px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Sidebars don't touch header</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Sidebar width</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">52px (collapsed)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Expands on hover</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Panel background</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">#fcfdff</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Near-white for light mode</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Border radius</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">12px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Inner corners only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Panel shadow</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-[10px]">0 12px 40px rgba(16,24,64,0.24)</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Elevation effect</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Left panel gap</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">16px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Between Panel 1 & 2</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono text-xs">Right panel gap</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">12px</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4">Between panels</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Usage Guidelines -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Usage Guidelines</h2>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <ul class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-2">
          <li>The shell layout uses <code>h-screen</code> and <code>overflow-hidden</code> to contain all content within the viewport</li>
          <li>The main content area uses <code>overflow-y-auto</code> for independent scrolling</li>
          <li>Sidebars are docked to edges with rounded inner corners only</li>
          <li>Use <code>custom-scroll</code> class for styled scrollbars</li>
          <li>CP does not use a footer - use the Floating Nav component instead</li>
          <li>Icons use Heroicons outline style at 24px with 6px padding</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</DocsLayout>
